hadiths[178]{hadithnumber,text}:
3962,"Yahya qattaan ne hamein Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahal khaibar se uski paidawar ke aadhey par mamla kya jo wahan se phalon aur kheti ki sura mein hasil hogi."
3963,"Ali-bin-Mus'hir ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar (ki zamin (us paidawar ke aadhey hissey par di jo wahan se phalon aur kheti ki sura mein hasil hogi. aap apni beeviyon ko har saal aik so (100) wasq detey, assi ( 80 ( wasq khajoor ke aur bees wasq jau ke.iske baad jab khaibar ki taqseem Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki zimme-dari mein aai to unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ko ikhtiyar diya ke unke liye zamin aur pani ka hissa muqarrar kar diya jaey ya unko har saal ( muqarrara ( wasq mil janey ki zamaanat dein. to unka (un donon mein se intikhab karne mein) aapasii ikhtilaf ho gaya. unmein se kuchh ne zamin aur pani ko muntakhab kiya aur kuchh ne har saal ( muqarrara ( wasq leney pasand kiye. Hazrat Hafsa aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anhuma) unmein se thin jinhoney zamin aur pani ko chunaa ."
3964,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahale khaibar ke sath wahan ki kheti aur phalon ki paidawar ke aadhey hissey par mamla ( kheti baadi ke kaam kaaj ka muaahida ( kiya. padhi. aagey Ali-bin-Mus'hir ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur unhon-ne ye zikr nahi kiya ke Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anhunna) unmein se thin jinhoney zamin aur pani ko intikhab kiya aur kaha : unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ko ikhtiyar diya ke unke liye zamin khas kar di jaey. aur unhon-ne pani ka ( bhi) zikr nahi kiya."
3965,"Usama-bin-Zaid Lesi ne mujhey Naafe se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab khaibar fateh hua to yahood ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki ke aap unhein is shart par wahin rehane dein. ke wo log wahan se hasil honey wale phalon aur ghalley ki paidawar ke aadhe hissey par kaam karein. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main tumhen is shart par jab tak ham chaahein gey rehney deta hun. phir Ubaidullah se riwayat ki hui ibne-Numair aur ibne-Mus'hir ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, aur is mein ye izafa kiya : khaibar ki paidawar ke nisf phalon ko) ghaneematon ke) hisson ke mutabiq taqseem kiya jata tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khums letey they."
3966,"Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne khaibar ke nakhlistaan aur zameenein is shart par khaibar ke yahudiyon ke sipurd kin ke wo apne amwaal laga kar us (ki zaminon aur baaghon ki dekh bhaal aur kheti baadi) ka kaam kaaj karengey aur uski paidawar ka aadha hissey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hoga."
3967,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne yahood aur nasara ko sarzameen hijaaz se jilaa watan kiya. aur ye ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar par ghalba hasil kiya to aap ne yahood ko wahan se nikalney ka irada farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke is par ghalba pa leney ke baad wo zamin izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah , iske rasool aur musalmanon ki thi. aap ne yahood ko wahan se nikalney ka irada kiya to yahood ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki ke aap unhein is shart par wahin rehney dein ke wo kaam ( baaghon aur kheton ki nigahdaasht aur kaasht ( ki zimme-dari ley lengey aur aadha phal ( paidawar ( unka hoga, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : ham jab tak chaahein gey tumhen wahan rehney dengey. phir wo wahin rahe yahan tak ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein teemaa aur areehaa ki taraf jilaa watan kar diya."
3968,"Ata ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi bhi musalman (jo) darakht lagaata hai, usmein se jo bhi khaya jaey wo uske liye sadqa hota hai, aur is mein se jo chori kya jaey wo uske liye sadqa hota hai aur jangli janwar usmein se jo kha jayen wo bhi uske liye sadqa hota hai aur jo parindey kha jayen wo bhi uske liye sadqa hota hai aur koi usmein ( kisi tarah ki) kami nahi karta magar wo uske liye sadqa hota hai."
3969,"Leis ne hamein abu-Zubair se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Umme- mubashshir ansariya (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan unke nakhlistaan mein tashrif le gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : ye khajoor ke darakht kis ne lagaey hain, kisi musalman ne ya kaafir ne? unhon-ne kaha : balke musalman ne. to aap ne farmaya : jo musalman darakht lagata hai ya kheti karta hai, phir usmein se insan, chaupaya ya koi bhi) janwar ( khata hai to wo uske liye sadqa hota hai."
3970,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim aur ibne-abi Khalaf ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Rauh ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jo bhi musalman aadmi darakht lagata hai aur kheti karta hai, phir us se koi jangli janwar, parinda ya koi bhi khaaey to uske liye usmein ajr hai. ibne-abi Khalaf ne (ya ke baghair ( parinda koi cheez kaha."
3971,"mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Umme- Mabad (Raziallahu anhu)) khaleeda , Hazrat Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) ki ahliya , unki dusri kunniyat Umme- mubashshir bhi thi) ke paas baagh mein tashrif le gaey to aap ne puchha : Umme- Mabad ! ye khajoor ke darakht kis ne lagaey hain, kisi musalman ne ya kaafir ne ? unhon-ne kaha : balke musalman ne. aap ne farmaya : jo bhi musalman darakht lagata hai, phir usmein se koi insan, chaupaya aur parinda nahi khata magar wo uske liye qiyamat ke din tak sadqa hota hai."
3972,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Hafs bin Ghiyas ne hadis bayan ki, neez abu-Kuraib aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne abu-Muawia se riwayat ki, aur Amr Naqid ne kaha : hamein Ammar bin-Muhammad ne hadis bayan ki, neez abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein ibne- Fuzel ne hadis bayan ki, un sab ( Hafs , abu-Muawia , Ammar aur ibne- Fuzel ( ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Sufiyan ( waastii ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. Amr ( Nafiz ( ne Ammar se riwayat ki hui riwayat main aur abu-Kuraib ne abu-Muawia se riwayat ki hui apni riwayat mein kaha : Umme- mubashshir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, ibne- Fuzel ki riwayat mein hai : Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi se riwayat hai, abu-Muawia se Ishaq ki riwayat mein hai, unhon-ne kaha : kabhi unhon-ne ( abu-Muawia ( ne kaha : Umme- mubashshir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aur kabhi-kabhi unhon-ne ( Umme- mubashshir (Raziallahu anhu)) nahi kaha, un sab ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai, padhi. ( aagey ( Ata, aur abu-Zubair aur Amr-bin-Dinar ki hadis (3968 - 3971) ki tarah hai."
3973,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi musalman nahi jo darakht lagaey ya kaasht kaarii karey, phir us se koi parinda , insan ya chaupaaya khaaey magar iske badley mein uske liye sadqa hoga."
3974,"Aban bin Yazeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Qatada ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ansar ki aik aurat Umme- mubashshir (Raziallahu anhu) ke nakhlistan mein dakhil huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye khajoor ke darakht kis ne lagaey hain, kisi musalman ne ya kisi kaafir ne ? un logon ne kaha : musalman ne. padhi. ( aagey ( un sab ki hadis ki tarah hai."
3975,"ibne- Wahab ne hamein ibne-Juraij se khabar di ke abu-Zubair ne unhein Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum ne apne bhai ko phal becha hai. neez abu-Zamra ne hamein ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum apne bhai ko phal becho aur wo kisi qudrati aafat ka shikar ho jaey to tumharey liye halal nahi ke tum us se kuchh wsool karo. tum nahaq apne bhai ka maal kis bina par wsool karogey."
3976,abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki
3977,"Ismail bin Jafar ne Humaid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rang badalney tak khajoor ka phal bechney se mana farmaya, ham ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : iske rang badalney se kya murad hai? unhon-ne kaha : wo surkh ho jaey aur zard ho jaey, tumhari kya raey hai agar Allah Taala ne phal rok diya, to tum kis buniyad par apne bhai ka maal apne liye halal samjhogey?"
3978,"Imam Malik ne Humaid Taweel se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rang pakadney se pahley phal ke saudey se mana farmaya, logon ne puchha : rang pakadney se kya murad hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : wo surkh ho jaey aur kaha : jab Allah Taala phalon se mahroom kar de to tum kis buniyad par apne bhai ka maal apne liye halal samjhogey?"
3979,Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad ne Humaid ke waastey se Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar Allah Taala usey baar-aawar na karey to tum mein se koi apne bhai ke maal ko kis buniyad par apne liye halal samjheyga?
3980,"Bishr-bin-hakam , Ibrahim-bin-Dinar aur abdul-jabbaar-bin Alaa se riwayat hai, alfaz Bishr ke hain, sab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Humaid Aaraj se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-ateeq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aafat se pahunchne waley nuqsan ki sura mein) qeemat ( saaqit (khatm) kar dene ka hukm diya hai. Abu-Ishaq Ibrahim ne, wo Imam Muslim ke shagird hain, kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Bishr ne bhi Sufiyan se yahi hadis bayan ki."
3981,"Leis ne hamein Bukair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ayaaz-bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein aik aadmi ka un phalon mein nuqsan ho gaya jo usney khareedey they. iska qarz badh gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is par sadqa karo. logon ne is par sadqa kiya lekin wo bhi qarz ki adaaeygi ( jitni maaliyat ( tak na pahuncha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske qarz daaron se farmaya : jo tumhen mil jaey, wo ley lo, tumharey liye iske ilawa aur kuchh nahi."
3982,Amr-bin-Haris ne Bukair-bin-Ash'ajj se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
3983,"Umra-binte-Abdur-Rehman (bin-Auf) ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne darwazey ke paas jhagdaa karne walon ki awaz suni. un donon ki aawaazein buland thin aur unmein se aik doosrey se kuchh kami karne ki aur kisi cheez mein narmi ki darkhaast kar raha tha. aur wo ( doosra ( keh raha tha : Allah ki qism ! main aisa nahi karunga . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un donon ke paas bahar tashrif le gaey aur farmaney lagey : Allah (ke naam ( par qism uthaney wala kahan hai ke wo neki ka kaam nahi karega? usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! main hun, is shakhs ke liye wahi sura hai jo ye pasand kare. (wo fauran apne bhai ka mutalba maan gaya.)"
3984,"Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Kab-bin-Malik ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein, masjid mein, ibne- abi-Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) se qarz ka mutalba kiya jo unke zimmey tha to unki aawaazein buland ho gaien. yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghar ke andar unki aawaazein sunein to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki taraf gaey yahan tak ke aap ne apne hujrey ka parda hataya aur Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko awaz di : Kab ! unhon-ne kaha : hazir hun, aey Allah ke rasool ! aap ne apne hath se unhein ishara kiya ke apne qarz ka aadha hissey maaf kar do. Kab ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! kar diya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (doosrey se) farmaya : utho aur iska qarz chuka do."
3985,"Usman-bin-Umar ne hamein khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Yunus ne Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Kab-bin-Malik se riwayat ki ke unhein Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke unhon-ne ibne- abi-Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) se apne qarz ka mutalba kiya. padhi. ( aagey ( ibne- Wahab ki hadis ki tarah hai."
3986,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Hurmuz ne Abdullah-bin-Kab-bin-Malik se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unka kuchh maal Abdullah-bin-abi-Hadrad Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ke zimmey tha. wo unhein miley to Kab (Raziallahu anhu) unke sath lag gaey. unki aapasi takraar hui yahan tak ke unki aawaazein buland ho gain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka unke paas se guzar hua to aap ne farmaya : Kab ! phir aap ne apne hath se ishara kiya, maano aap farma rahe they ke aadha ley lo, chunanche unhon-ne us maal mein se jo us ( ibne- abii-Hadrad Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) ke zimmey tha, aadha ley liya aur aadha chhod diya."
3987,"Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Abu-Bakar-bin-Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Hazam ne khabar di ke unhein Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez ne khabar di, unhein Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris-bin-Hisham ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. ya (is tarah kaha : ( maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. aap farma rahe they : jisne apna maal joon ka toon us shakhs ke paas paya jo muflis ho chuka hai. ya us insan ke paas jo muflis ho chuka hai. to wo dusron ki nisbat us (maal (ka zyada haq-daar hai."
3988,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hushaim ne khabar di, (isi tarah) Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh donon ne Lais-bin-Sad se riwayat ki aur (usi tarah) abu-Rabee aur Yahya bin Habib haarisi ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hadis bayan ki abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis sunai Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne bayan kya : hamein abdul-wahaab, Yahya-bin-Saeed (al-Qattan) aur Hafs bin Ghiyas , sab ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, isi sanad ke sath Zuhair ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, albatta unmein se ibne- Rumeh ne apni riwayat mein kaha : jis kisi aadmi ko muflis qarar diya gaya ho."
3989,"ibne-abi-Husain ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke unhein Abu-Bakar-bin-Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Hazam ne khabar di ke unhein Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez ne Abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman ki (riwaayat ki hui ( hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki (riwaayat ki hui ( hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us shakhs ke barey mein riwayat ki jo kangaal ho jaey, jab uske paas saman miley aur us ne usmein se kuch istemaal na kiya ho, ( farmaya : ( to wo uske Malik ka hai, jisne usey farokht kiya tha."
3990,"Shoba ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhein ne nazar-bin-Anas se, unhon-ne Bashir-bin-naheek se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jab koi aadmi muflis ho jaey aur koi aadmi ( uske paas ( apna maal jiyon ka tiyon paaey to wo uska zyada haq daar hai."
3991,Saeed aur Hisham donon ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki aur kaha : to wo (doosrey ( qarz-chaahne walon ki nisbat us (maal (ka zyada haqdaar hai.
3992,Iraak-bin-Malik ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab koi aadmi muflis qarar diya jaey aur (kisi bechney waale) shakhs ko iske yahaan apna saman jiyon ka tiyon mil jaey to wo uska zyada haqdaar hai.
3993,"Mansoor ne hamein Rabai-bin-Hirash se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Huzefa (bin-yamaan (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum se pahley logon mein se aik aadmi ki Rooh ka farishton ne istiqbaal kiya to unhon-ne puchha : kya tu ney koi neki ki hai? usne kaha : nahi, unhon-ne kaha : yad kar, usne kaha : main ( duniya mein) logon ke sath qarz ka mamla karta to apne khaadimon ko hukm deta tha ke wo tangdast ko mohlat dein aur khush-haal se narmi bartein .) unhon-ne ( kaha : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya hai : (tum bhi) iske sath narmi ka sulook karo."
3994,"Nuaim-bin-abi-Hind ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Huzefa aur Hazrat Abu-Masood ( Ansari ( (Raziallahu anhu) ikatthey huey to Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aik aadmi izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke huzoor pesh hua to Allah ne puchha : tu ney kya amal kiya? usne kaha : maine koi neki nahi ki, siwaey iske ke main maaldaar aadmi tha, main logon se us (mein se diye huey qarz (ka mutalba karta to maaldaar se khush dili se qabool karta aur tang dast se darguzar ( mazeed mohlat deta ya na de sakta to maaf ( karta. farmaya : (tum bhi) mere bandey se darguzar karo. (ye sun kar) Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is tarah farmatey huey suna hai."
3995,"abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se, unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : aik aadmi faut hua aur jannat mein dakhil hua to us se kaha gaya : to kya amal karta tha? kaha is ne khud yad kiya ya usey yad karaya gaya. padhi. usne kaha : (aey mere parwardigar ! ( main logon se ( qarz par) khareed w farokht karta tha, to main tang dast ko mohlat deta aur sikka aur naqdi wsool karne mein narmi karta tha. to uski maghfirat kar di gaee is par Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine bhi yahi hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi."
3996,"Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke paas uska aik banda laya gaya jis ko us ne maal diya tha. to Allah Taala ne us se puchha tu ney duniya mein kya amal kiya? aur Allah se kuchh nahi chipa saktey. bandey ne kaha aey mere Malik ! to ne apna maal mujh ko diya tha mein logon ke hath bechtaa tha aur meri aadat thi darguzar karne ki (aur maaf karne ki) to main aasani karta tha maaldaar par aur mohlat deta tha naadaar ko. tab izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya phir main to zyada laaiq hon maaf karne ke liye tujh se, darguzar karo mere bandey se. phir Aqba-bin-Aamir Juhni aur Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ham ne aisa hi suna hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh Mubarak se."
3997,Hazrat abi-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum se pahley aik shakhs ka hisab hua to uski koi neki na nikli. magar itni ke wo logon se mamla karta tha aur maaldaar tha to apne ghulaamon ko hukm karta naadaar ko maaf kar deney kaa. tab Allah Taala ne farmaya ham zyada haq rakhtey hain maaf karne ka tujh se aur hukm diya ke maaf karo iske gunahon ko .
3998,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aik shakhs logon ko qarz diya karta aur wo apne naukaron se kehta jo muflis ho usko maaf kar dena shayad Allah Taala iske badley ham ko maaf kare. phir wo Allah Taala se mila Allah ne usko bakhsh diya.
3999,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di ke unhein Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah."
4000,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada se riwayat ki ke Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne aik qarz daar ko talash kiya to wo unse chhup gaya. phir ( baad mein) unhon-ne usey pa liya to usne kaha : main tang dast hun. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qasam? us ne jawab diya : Allah ki qism ! unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jisey ye baat achi lagey ke Allah Taala usey qiyamat ke din ki sakhtiyon se nijat de to wo tang dast ko sahoolat de ya usey maaf kar de."
4001,Jareer-bin-Haazim ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
4002,Aaraj (Abdur-Rehman-bin-Hurmuz madni) ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ghani aadmi ka taal matol karna zulm hai. aur jab tum mein se kisi ko kisi maal daar (se wsooli) par lagaya jaey to usey lag jana chahiye
4003,Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. padhi. usi ki tarah.
4004,"Wakee aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bach janey waley pani ko farokht karne se mana farmaya."
4005,"Rooh-bin-Ubada ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne oont ki jufti farokht karne, kaasht-kaarii ke liye pani aur zamin ko farokht karne se mana farmaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne in saari baton se mana farmaya hai."
4006,Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zayed pani ko na rokaa jaey ke uske zariey se ghaas roki jaey.
4007,"ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zayed pani na roko ke uske zariey se tum ghaas rok do."
4008,"Hilal-bin-Usaama ne khabar di ke abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne unhein bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zayed pani ko farokht na kiya jaey ke uske zariey se ghaas ko farokht kiya jaey."
4009,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat, zaaniya ke muaawzey aur kaahin ke nazraaney se mana farmaya."
4010,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-rumeh ne Lais-bin-Sad se riwayat ki, neez abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis sunai, un donon ( Lais-bin-Sad aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ( ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki. ibne- Rumeh ki riwayat ki hui Leis ki hadis mein hai ke unhon ( Abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman ( ne Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se sama'at ki."
4011,"Muhammad-bin-Yousuf se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Saaib-bin-Yazeed se suna, wo Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : badtareen kamaai zaaniya ki ujrat , kuttey ki qeemat aur pachhney lagaaney waley ki kamaai hai."
4012,"Auzai ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Ibrahim-bin-qaariz ne Saaib-bin-Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan ki, aap ne farmaya : kuttey ki qeemat khabees ( napak aur gandi ( hai. zaaniya ki ujrat khabees hai aur pachhney lagaaney waley ki kamaai khabees hai."
4013,Mamar ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4014,"Hisham ne hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Ibrahim-bin-Abdullah ne Saaib-bin-Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4015,"abu-Zubair se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se kuttey aur billi ki qeemat ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is se jhidak kar rokaa hai."
4016,Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kutton ko mar dene ka hukm diya.
4017,"Ubaidullah ne hamein Naafe ke hawale se Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kutton ko maarney ka hukm diya. aap ne unhein maarney ke liye Madina ke aas-paas mein aadmi rawaana kiye."
4018,"Ismail-bin-Umayya ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kutton ko maarney ka hukm detey they. main Madina aur uske aas-paas mein talash karta. ham koi kutta na chhodtey magar usey mar daltey. yahan tak ke ham dehaat se aaney wali aurat ke kuttey ko bhi, jo iske peechhey aa jata tha, qatl kar detey they."
4019,"Amr-bin-Dinar ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shikaari kuttey , bakriyon ya maweshiyon (ki hifazat) ke kuttey ke siwa (baqi) tamam kutton ko mar dalney ka hukm diya. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : ya khet ki hifazat karne waley kuttey ke. to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bila shubah Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka khet bhi hai."
4020,"abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein kutton ko mar dalney ka hukm diya yahan tak ke koi aurat jangal se apne kuttey ke sath aati to ham us kuttey ko bhi mar daltey. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein unko maarney se mana kar diya aur farmaya : tum (aankhon ke uper) do (safaid) nuqton waley kaley siyah kuttey ko na chhodo ,bila shubah wo shaitan hai."
4021,"Muaz Anbari ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Tayyah se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Mutarif-bin-Abdullah se suna aur unhon-ne Hazrat ( Abdullah ( bin-mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kutton ko maarney ka hukm diya, phir farmaya : un logon ka kutton se kya waasta hai? baad mein aap ne shikaari kuttey aur bakriyon (ki hifazat ( waley kuttey ki ijazat de di."
4022,"Yahya-bin-Habib ne kaha : hamein Khalid-bin-Haaris ne hadis bayan ki Muhammad-bin-Hatim ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hadis sunai Muhammad-bin-Waleed ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki. Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein nazar ne khabar di Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Wahab-bin-Jareer ne hadis bayan ki, ( Khalid-bin-Haaris , Yahya-bin-Saeed , Muhammad-bin-Jafar , nazar aur Wahab-bin-Jareer ( sab ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki. ibne- Hatim ne apni hadis mein kaha : Yahya se riwayat hai, (aur aagey ye kaha : (aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bakriyon ki rakhwaalii , shikar aur khet ki hifazat karne waley kuttey ki ijazat de di."
4023,"Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne maweshiyon ki hifazat karne waley aur shikaari kuttey ke siwa kutta paala uske ajr mein se har roz do qirat kam hongey."
4024,"Zohri ne Salim se, unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jisne shikar ya maweshiyon ke kuttey ke siwa kutta rakha uske ajr mein se har roz do qirat kam hongey."
4025,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne shikar ya maweshiyon ke kuttey ke siwa kutta rakha uske amal mein se har roz do qirat kam hongey."
4026,Muhammad-bin-abi-Hurmala ne Saalim-bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne maweshiyon ke kuttey ya shikar ke kuttey ke siwa kutta rakha to iske amal se har roz aik qirat kam hoga. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya kheti ke kuttey (ke siwa).
4027,"Hanzala-bina-abi-Sufiyan ( Aswad-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-safwaan-bin-Umayya) ne Salim se, unhon-ne apne walid (Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jisne shikaari kuttey ya maweshiyon ke kuttey ke siwa kutta paala iske amal se har roz do qirat kam hongey. Salim ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they : ya kheti ke kuttey (ke siwa). aur wo (khud) kheti ke Malik they. (is liye unhein ye baat yad thi.)"
4028,"Umar-bin-Hamza-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jin ghar walon ne maweshiyon (ki hifazat ( waley kuttey ya shikaari kuttey ke siwa kutta rakha , to unke amal se har roz do qirat kam hongey."
4029,"abu-Hakam se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, aap ne farmaya : jisne kheti ya bakriyon (ki hifazat) ya shikar ke kuttey ke siwa kutta rakha iske ajr mein se har roz aik qirat kam hoga."
4030,"abu-Taahir aur Hurmala ne kaha : hamein ibne-Wahab ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne kutta paala jo shikaari hai, na maweshiyon ke liye hai aur na hi zamin ke liye. uske ajr se har roz do qirat kam hongey. abu-Taahir ki hadis mein ''na zamin ke liye'' ke alfaz nahi hain."
4031,"imam Zohri ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne maweshiyon , shikar ya kheti (ki hifazat karne) waley kuttey ke siwa (koii aur) kutta rakha uske ajr se har roz aik qirat kam hoga. imam Zohri ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke us qaul ka tazkira kiya gaya to unhon-ne kaha : Allah Taala , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) par raham farmaai ! wo (khud) khet ke Malik they. ( unhon-ne ye baat zabt ki.)"
4032,"Hisham dustwaai ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Salma se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne kutta rakha , iske amal se har roz aik qirat kam hoga. siwaey kheti ya maweshiyon (ki hifazat karne) waley kuttey ke."
4033,"Auzai ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4034,Harab ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4035,"abu-Razeen ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne (aisa) kutta rakha jo shikar ya bakriyon ka kutta nahi hai to uske amal se har roz aik qirat kam hoga."
4036,"Imam Malik ne Yazeed-bin-khaseefa se riwayat ki ke unhein Saaib-bin-Yazeed ne bataya ke unhon-ne Sufiyan-bin-abi-Zuhair (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aura wo shanua qabeeley se talluq rakhney waale, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi they, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jisne kutta rakha jo usey kheti aur than ( waley janwaron ki hifazat (ka fayda nahi deta. to uske amal se har roz aik qirat kam hoga. (Saaib ne) kaha : kya aap ne khud ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan , is masjid ke rab ki qism !"
4037,"Ismail ne hamein Yazeed-bin-khuseefa se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Saaib-bin-Yazeed ne khabar di ke unke paas Sufiyan-bin-abi Zuhair-shanie (Raziallahu anhu)) qabila shanu se talluq rakhney waale) aaey aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. usi ki tarah."
4038,"Ismail-bin-Jafar ne hamein Humaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se pachhney  (seengi) lagaaney waley ki kamaai ke barey mein puchha gaya to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhney lagwaaey, aapko abu-Taiba ne pachhney lagaey to aap ne usey ghalley se do saa dene ka hukm diya. aur uske maalikon se baat ki to unhon-ne uske mahsool (tex) mein kuchh kami (kami) kar di aur aap ne farmaya : tum log jo ilaaj karwaao usmein se behtreen seengi lagwaanaa hai ya ( farmaya : ( ye tumharey behtreen ilaajon mein se hai."
4039,"Marwan fazari ne hamein Humaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se seengi lagaaney waley ki kamaai ke barey mein puchha gaya. padhi. aagey usi ki tarah bayan kiya, magar unhon-ne kaha : bila shubah sabse afzal jiske zariey se tum ilaaj karao , pachhney lagwaana aur qust-al-bahri (ka istemal) hai. aur tum apne bachchon ko gala daba kar (mal-kar) takleef na do."
4040,"Shoba ne hamein Humaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey aik pachhney lagaaney waley ghulam ko bulaya. us ne aapko pachhney lagaey to aap ne usey aik saa , aik mudd ya do mudd dene ka hukm diya aur uske mutaalliq (iske maalikon se) baat ki to iske mahsool (tex) mein kami kar di gaee."
4041,Taaus ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhney lagwaaey aur seengi lagaaney waley ko uski ujrat di aur aap ne naak ke zariey se dawaa li.
4042,"Shabi ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : banu-biyaaza ke aik ghulam ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pachhney lagaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey uski ujrat di aur aap ne uske Malik se baat ki to usne iske mahsool (tex) mein kuchh kami kar di aur agar ye ( ujrat ( haram hoti to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko na detey."
4043,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap Madina mein khutba de rahe they, aap ne farmaya logo ! Allah Taala sharab (ki hurmat (ke barey mein ishara farma raha hai aur shayad Allah Taala jald hi iske barey mein koi ( qatae ( hukm nazil kar de. jiske paas us ( sharab ( mein se kuchh maujood hai wo usey bech de aur us se fayda utha ley. kaha : phir ham ne thoda hi arsa us aalim mein guzara ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne yaqinan sharab ko haram kar diya hai. jis shakhs tak ye aayat pahunchey aur uske paas us ( sharab ( mein se kuchh ( hissey baqi ( hai to na wo usey piye aur na farokht kare. kaha : logon ke paas jo bhi sharab thi wo usey lekar Madina ke rastey mein nikal aaey aur usey baha diya."
4044,"Suwed-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hafs-bin-Maisra ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se hadis sunai, unhon-ne  misr walon ke aadmi,  Abdur-Rehman-bin-Wala se riwayat ki ke wo Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur mujhey abu-Taahir ne hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz unhi ke hain. padhi. : hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di : mujhey Malik-bin-Anas aur dusron ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne . padhi. misr ke baashindon mein se,  Abdur-Rehman-bin-Wala-sabai se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se us cheez ke barey mein sawal kiya jo angoor se nichodi jati hai. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sharab ka aik mishkeeza hadiya kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : kya tumhen ilm hai ke Allah Taala ne usey haram qarar diya hai? us ne jawab diya : nahi, iske baad us ne aik insan se sargoshi ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha : tum ne us se kya sargoshi ki hai? us ne jawab diya : maine us se ye farokht karne ko kaha hai. to aap ne farmaya : jis ( Allah ( ne iska peenaa haram kiya hai us ne uska Sauda bhi haram qarar diya hai. kaha : is par us shakhs ne mishkeezey ka munh khol diya yahan tak ke jo usmein tha, bah gaya."
4045,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Wala se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
4046,"Mansoor ne abu-Zuhaa ( Muslim-bin-sabeeh ( se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab sura Baqra ke aakhiri hissey ki aayatein nazil huin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif ley gaey. aap ne logon ke samney unki tilawat ki, phir aap ne sharab ki tijarat se bhi mana farma diya."
4047,"Aamash ne ( abu-Zuhaa ( Muslim se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab sood ke barey mein sura Baqra ki aakhiri aayatein nazil ki gain , kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid ki taraf tashrif le gaey aur aap ne sharab ki tijarat ko bhi haram qarar diya."
4048,"Leis ne hamein Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko fateh Makka ke saal , jab aap Makka hi mein they, farmatey huey suna : bila shubah Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sharab , murdar , khinzeer aur buton ke saudey haram qarar diye hai. kaha gaya : aey Allah ke rasool ! murdar janwar ki charbi ke barey mein aap ki kya raey hai? us se kashtiyon (ke takhtey ( ko raughan kiya jata hai. aur chamdon ko narm kiya jata hai. aur log us se charagh jalaatey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, wo haram hai. phir usi waqt , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah yahood ko halaak karey ! Allah ne jab unke liye un janwaron ki charbi haram ki to unhon-ne usey pighlaayaa , phir usey farokht kiya aur uski qeemat lekar khaai."
4049,"abdul-hameed se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Ata ne mujhey likh bheja ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : maine fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. padhi. aagey Leis ki hadis ki tarah hai."
4050,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Amr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Taaus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko itlaa mili ke Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne sharab farokht ki hai to unhon-ne kaha : Allah Samra ko halaak karey ! kya wo nahi janta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah yahood par laanat karey ! (ke ( un par charbi haram ki gaee to unhon-ne usey pighlaayaa aur farokht kiya?"
4051,Rooh-bin-Qasim ne Amr-bin-Dinar se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4052,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey ibne-Shahab ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se khabar di ke unhon-ne unhein ( ibne-Shahab ko) Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan ki, aap ne farmaya : Allah yahood ko halaak karey ! Allah ne un par charbi haram ki to unhon-ne usey bechaa aur uski qeemat khaai."
4053,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah yahood ko halaak karey ! un par charbi haram ki gaee to unhon-ne usey becha aur uski qeemat khaai."
4054,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum soney ke iwaz soney ka Sauda na karo, siwaey-iske ke barabar-barabar ho aur usey aik doosrey se kam zyada na karo aur na tum chandi ka Sauda chandi ke iwaz karo, siwaey-iske ke barabar ho. aur usey aik doosrey se kam zyada na karo aur is mein se jo ghair maujood ho uska Sauda maujood ke iwaz na karo."
4055,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-Rumeh ne Leis se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke banu- Leis ke aik shakhs ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baat bayan kartey hain. Quteba ki riwayat mein hai : Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) chaley aur Naafe bhi sath they. aur ibne- Rumeh ki hadis mein hai : Naafe ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) chaley, main aur Lesi bhi unke sath they. yahan tak ke wo Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaey aur kaha is aadmi ne mujhey bataya hai ke aap hadis bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ka chandi ke iwaz saudey se mana farmaya hai magar ye ke barabar-barabar ho, aur soney ka soney ke iwaz saudey se ( mana farmaya ( siwaey-iske ke barabar-barabar ho? Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni do ungliyon se apni donon aankhon aur donon kanon ki taraf ishara kiya aur kaha : meri donon aankhon ne dekha aur mere donon kanon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : tum soney ke iwaz soney ka aur chandi ke iwaz chandi ka Sauda na karo magar ye ke barabar aur usey aik doosrey se kam zyada na karo aur is mein se kisi ghair maujood cheez ka maujood ke sath Sauda na karo, siwaey-iske ke haath ke haath ho."
4056,"Jareer-bin-Haazim , Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Ibne-Aun , sab ne Naafe se riwayat ki, Leis ki Naafe se, unki Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki tarah."
4057,Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum soney ka soney ke iwaz aur chandi ka chandi ke iwaz Sauda na karo magar ye ke wazan-b-wazn barabar-barabar ho.
4058,Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum aik Dinar ki do dinaron ke iwaz aur aik dirham ki do dirhamon ke iwaz Sauda na karo.
4059,"Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se khabar di aur unhon-ne Malik-bin-Aos-bin-hadsaan se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : main ( logon ke samney ( ye kehta hua aaya : ( soney ke iwaz ( dirhamon ka tabaadla kon karega? to Hazrat Talha-bin-Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, padhi. aur wo Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they. hamein apna sona dikhao , phir ( zara thahar ke) hamarey paas aana , jab hamara khaadim aayega to ham tumhen tumhari chandi (ke dirham ( de dengey. is par Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hargiz nahi, Allah ki qism ! tum unhein chandi do ya unka sona unhein wapas karo kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai : soney ke iwaz chandi (ka Sauda ( sood hai, siwaey-iske ke hathon-hath ( dast-badast (ho aur gandam ke iwaz gandam sood hai, siwaey-iske ke hathon-hath ho aur jau ke iwaz jau sood hai, siwaey-iske ke hathon-hath ho aur khajoor ke iwaz khajoor sood hai, siwaey-iske ke hathon-hath ho."
4060,ibne-Uena ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( riwayat bayan ki.
4061,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Sham  mein aik majlis mein tha jis mein Muslim-bin-Yasar bhi they. itney mein abu-Ash'as aaey to logon ne kaha : abu-Ash'as , (aa gaey ( maine kaha : ( achchha ( abu Ash'as ! wo baith gaey to maine unse kaha : hamarey bhai ! hamein Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis bayan kijiye . unhon-ne kaha : haan , ham ne aik jang ladi aur logon ke ameer Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) they, ham ne bahut se ghanimat ke maal hasil kiye. jo hamein ghaneemat mein mila usmein chandi ke bartan bhi they. Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik aadmi ko hukm diya ke wo unhein logon ko milney waley atiyaat (ke badley) mein farokht kar de. (jab atiyaat milein gey to qeemat us waqt daraahim ki sura mein ley li jaeygi) logon ne un (ko khareedney) mein jaldi ki. ye baat Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ko pahunchi to wo khadey huey aur kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap soney ke iwaz soney ki, chandi ke iwaz chandi ki, gandam ke iwaz gandam ki, jau ke iwaz jau ki, khajoor ke iwaz khajoor ki aur namak ke iwaz namak ke saudey se mana farma rahe they, siwaey-iske ke barabar-barabar , naqd ba-naqd ho. jisne zyada diya ya zyada liya to usne sood ka lein-dein kiya. (ye sun kar) logon ne jo liya tha wapas kar diya. Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye baat pahunchi to wo khutba dene ke liye khadey huey aur kaha : suno ! logon ka haal kya hai ! wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadisein bayan kartey hain, ham bhi aap ke paas hazir hotey aur aap ke sath rahtey they lekin ham ne aap se wo (hadisey) nahi sunein . is par Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho gaey, ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hua) Sara waqia dohraya aur kaha : ham wo hadisey zaroor bayan karengey jo ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunein , chahe Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) na-pasand karein. padhi. ya kaha : chahe unki naak khaak aalud ho. padhi. mujhey parwaa nahi ke main unke lashkar mein unke sath aik siyah raat bhi na rahoon . Hammad ne kaha : ye (kaha : (ya iske ham mana."
4062,abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki.
4063,"Khalid Hazza ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne abu-Ash'as se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : soney ke iwaz sona , chandi ke iwaz chandi , gandam ke iwaz gandam , jau ke iwaz jau , khajoor ke iwaz khajoor aur namak ke iwaz namak (ka lein-dein)  barabar-barabar aur naqd ba-naqd hai. jab asnaaf mukhtalif hon to jaisey chaho Sauda karo basharte ke wo dast badast ho.(hatho-hath)"
4064,"Ismail-bin-Muslim abdi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Mutwakkil naaji ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : soney ke iwaz sona , chandi ke iwaz chandi , gandam ke iwaz gandam , jau ke iwaz jau , khajoor ke iwaz khajoor aur namak ke iwaz namak (ka Sauda ( hathon-hath ho. jisne zyada diya ya zyada liya us ne sood ka lein-dein kiya, usmein leney wala aur dene wala barabar hain."
4065,"Sulaiman Rabai ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein abu-Mutwakkil naaji ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : soney ke iwaz soney (ka Sauda ( barabar ki tarah hai. padhi. ( aagey ( pichhli hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
4066,"Fuzel ke betey ( Muhammad ( ne hamein apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Zara' se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khajoor ke iwaz khajoor , gandam ke iwaz gandam , jau ke iwaz jau aur namak ke iwaz namak (ka Sauda ( dast badast (haath ke haath) ho. jisne zyada diya ya zyada liya us ne sood ka ( lein-dein ( kiya, siwaey-iske ke unki ajnaas (jins) alag-alag hon."
4067,Maharibi ne Fuzail-bin-ghazawaan se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne dast badast ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye.
4068,"ibne-abi-nu'aim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : soney ke iwaz soney ke saudey ham wazan aur usi jins ke saath hai aur chandi ke iwaz chandi ham wazan ke saath hai. jisne zyada diya ya zyada liya to wo sood hai."
4069,"Sulaiman-bi- Bilal ne hamein Musa-bin-abi Tameem se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Dinar se Dinar ke saudey mein unke darmyan izafa ( jaaiz ( nahi aur dirham se dirham ke tabaadley mein unke darmyan izafa ( jaaiz ( nahi."
4070,imam Malik-bin-Anas ne kaha : mujhey Musa-bin-abi Tameem ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4071,"Amr (bin-Dinar) ne abu-Minhaal se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere aik Shareek ne mausam (hajj ke mausam) tak ya Haj tak chandi udhaar farokht ki, wo mere paas aaya aur mujhey bataya to maine kaha : ye mamla durust nahi. usne kaha : maine wo bazar mein farokht ki hai aur usey kisi ne mere samney naqabile-qabool qarar nahi diya. is par main Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur unse puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey aur ham ye Sauda kiya kartey they, to aap ne farmaya : jo dast badast hai is mein koi harj nahi aur jo udhaar hai wo sood hai. Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jao aur unka karobar mujh se wasee hai, chunanche main unke paas aaya aur unse puchha to unhon-ne bhi usi ki tarah kaha."
4072,"Habib se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne abu-Minhaal se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se Dinar ka dirham se ya soney ka chandi se saudey ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se poochho , wo zyada jaanney waley hain, chunanche maine Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se poochho , wo zyada jaanney waley hain, phir donon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ke iwaz chandi ke udhaar saudey se mana farmaya."
4073,"Ibad-bin-awaam ne kaha : Yahya-bin-abi-Ishaq ne hamein khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-bakra ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ke iwaz chandi aur soney ke iwaz soney ke saudey se mana farmaya, siwaey-iske ke barabar barabar ho aur aap ne hamein hukm diya ke ham soney ke iwaz chandi jaisey chaahein khareedein aur chandi ke iwaz sona jaisey chaahein khareedein . kaha : is par aik aadmi ne unse sawal kiya aur kaha : dast badast ? to unhon-ne kaha : maine isi tarah suna hai."
4074,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne Yahya-bin-abi Ishaq se riwayat ki ke unhein Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-bakra ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein mana farmaya, padhi. ( aagey ( usi ki tarah hai."
4075,"Ali-bin-ribaah-lakhmee ne kaha : maine Hazrat fazaala-bin-Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas , jabke aap khaibar mein they, aik haar laya gaya, usmein nageeney they aur sona tha aur wo un maaley ghaneemat mein se tha jo farokht ki ja rahi thin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us soney ke barey mein hukm diya jo haar mein tha, to akeley usi ko alag kar diya gaya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon se (jo lein-dein kar rahe they) farmaya : soney ke iwaz sona barabar barabar wazan ka (khareedo aur becho)."
4076,"Leis ne hamein abu-Shujaa' Saeed-bin-Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Khalid-bin-abi-Imran se, unhon-ne hansh san'aani se aur unhon-ne Hazrat fazaala-bin-Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine khaibar ke din baarah Dinar mein aik haar khareedaa. usmein sona aur nageeney they. maine unhein alag-alag kiya to mujhey usmein baarah Dinar se zyada mil gaey. maine is baat ka tazkira Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kiya to aap ne farmaya : usey alag-alag karne se pahley farokht na kiya jaey."
4077,ibne-Mubarak ne Saeed-bin-Yazeed se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
4078,"jalaah-abu-Kaseer se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey hansh san'aani ne Hazrat fazaala-bin-Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : khaibar ke din ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, ham yahood ke sath do ya teen dinaaron ke iwaz aik auqiya soney ka Sauda kartey they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : soney ke iwaz soney ka Sauda na karo magar barabar-barabar wazan ke sath."
4079,"Aamir-bin-Yahya muaafiri ne hansh se khabar di ke unhon-ne kaha : ham aik ghazwey mein Hazrat fazaala-bin-Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they. mere aur mere sathiyon ke hissey mein aik haar aaya jis mein sona , chandi aur jawaahir they. maine usey kharidney ka irada kiya, chunanche maine Hazrat fazaala-bin-Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha : iska sona utaar lo aur isey aik paldey mein rakho aur apna sona doosrey paldey mein rakho, phir barabar barabar ke siwa na lo (kyonke) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, aap farma rahe they : jo Allah aur yaum aakhirat par eman rakhta hai. wo (is tarah ke saudey mein) barabari ka muamla karey,barabari ke siwa hargiz na ley."
4080,"basar-bin-Saeed ne Mamar-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne gandam ka aik saa de kar apna ghulam bheja aur kaha : usey bech do, phir us (ki qeemat ( se ''jau'' khareed laao. ghulam gaya aur) gandam ke saa ke iwaz ( aik saa aur saa se kuchh zyada (jau) ley aaya, jab wo Mamar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to unhein ye baat batai , to Hazrat Mamar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : tum ne ye kaam kyon kiya? jao aur usey wapas karo aur barabari ke siwa kuchh na lo. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna karta tha, aap farmatey they : ghalley ke iwaz ghalley ka sauda barabar-barabar ka hai. kaha : un dinon hamari khuraak jau ki thi. unse kaha gaya : wo to us ( gandam (ka jaisa nahi hai. (yani do alag jinsein hain, isliye tafaazil (farq) jaaiz hai.) unhon-ne kaha : mujhey khadsha (dar) hai ke wo iske mushabeh (similar) hogi."
4081,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne hamein abdul-Majeed-bin-Suhail-bin-Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu- Adi se talluq rakhney waley aik Ansari ko bheja aur usey khaibar ka aamil muqarrar kiya, wo janeeb (umda qism ki) khajoor lekar aaya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha : kya khaibar ki tamam khajoor isi tarah ki hai? usne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! Allah ki qism ! nahi. ham mili jhuli khajoor ke do saa ke iwaz (umda khajoor ka ( aik saa khareedtey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aisa na karo balke yaksan khareedo, becho  ya phir usey bech do aur uski qeemat se dusri qisam khareed lo, isi tarah wazan (ke zariey se lein-dein karna ho to bhi barabar hona zaroori ( hai."
4082,"Imam Malik ne abdul-Majeed-bin-Suhail-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko khaibar ka aamil muqarrar kiya. wo aap ke paas janeeb (umda qism ki) khajoor ley aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha : kya khaibar ki tamam khajoor isi tarah ki hai? usne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ya Rasulullah ! nahi. ham ( mili-jhuli khajoor ke) do saa ke iwaz iska aik saa aur teen ke iwaz do saa letey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aisa na karo, mili-jhuli khajoor ko dirhamon ke iwaz bech do, phir dirhamon se janeeb (umda) khajoor khareed lo."
4083,"Ishaq-bin-Mansur ne kaha : hamein Yahya bin Saleh w haazi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Muawiya bin Salam ne hadis sunai. neez Muhammad-bin Suhel tameemi aur Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman daarmi ne. padhi. alfaz donon ke yahi hain. padhi. donon ne mujhey Yahya bin Hassan se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Muawiya bin Salam ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Aqba bin abdul-Ghaafir se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) barni khajoor lekar aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha : ye kahan se laey ho? to Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hamarey paas raddi khajoor thi, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khaney ke liye usey 2 saa ke iwaz (iske ( aik saa se bech diya. to us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey afsos hua ! to ye sood hi hai, aisa na karo balke jab tum khajoor khareedna chaho to usey (raddi khajoor ko) dusri (naqdi wghaira ke iwaz ki gai) saude ke zariey se bech do, phir us (ki qeemat) se (doosri qism) khareed lo. ibne-Sahal ne apni hadis mein us waqt ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
4084,"abu-Nazara ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas khajoor laai gaee to aap ne farmaya : ye khajoor hamari khajoor mein se nahi. is par aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! ham ne apni khajoor ke 2 saa us khajoor ke aik saa ke iwaz bechey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye sood hai, usey wapas karo, phir hamari khajoor (naqdi ke iwaz) farokht karo aur (uski qeemat se) hamarey liye ye khajoor khareedo."
4085,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein hamein (hamarey hissey mein) aam khajoor di jati thi aur wo mili-juli khajoor hoti thi to ham iske 2 saa ke iwaz aik saa ka Sauda kartey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi to aap ne farmaya : khajoor ke 2 saa aik saa ke badley ( jaaiz ( nahi, gehun ke 2 saa aik saa ke badley ( jaaiz ( nahi aur na aik dirham 2 dirhamon ke badley ( jaaiz hai.)"
4086,"Saeed Jurairi ne abu-Nazara se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Dinar w dirham ya soney chandi ke tabadley ke barey mein sawal kya to unhon-ne kaha : kya ye dast-badast hai? maine jawab diya : ji haan , unhon-ne kaha : ismein koi harj nahi. maine Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ko khabar di, maine kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Dinar w dirham ya soney-chandi ke tabaadley ke barey mein sawal kya tha to unhon-ne kaha tha : kya dast-badast hai? maine jawab diya tha : haan, to unhon-ne kaha tha : ismein koi harj nahi (unhon-ne aik hi jins ki sura mein barabari ki shart lagaey baghair usey yun hi jaaiz qarar diya.) unhon ( abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : kya unhon-ne ye baat kahi hai? ham unki taraf likhengey to wo tumhen (ghair mashroot jawaz ka ( ye fatwa nahi dengey. Allah ki qasam! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khadimon se koi khajoorein lekar aaya to aap ne unhen na pehchana aur farmaya : aisa lagta hai ke ye hamari sarzameen ki khajooron mein se nahi hain. usne kaha is saal hamari zamin ki khajooron mein. padhi. ya hamari khajooron mein. padhi. koi cheez ( kharabi ( thi, maine ye (umda khajoorein ( le lin aur badley mein kuchh zyada de din, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne 2 guna din, tum ne sood ka len-den kya, iske qareeb ( bhi) mat jao, jab tumhen apni khajoor ke barey mein kisi cheez ( naqs wghaira) ka shak ho to usey farokht karo, phir khajoor mein se tum jo chahtey ho (naqdi ke badley) khareed lo."
4087,"Dawud ne hamein abu-Nazara se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se sona chandi ke tabaadley ke barey mein puchha to un donon ne usmein koi harj na dekha. main Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha hua tha to maine unse us tabaadley ke barey mein poochha, to unhon-ne kaha : (eik hi jins ke tabaadley mein) jo izafa hoga wo sood hai. maine un donon ke qaul ki bina par (jis mein unhon-ne aisi koi shart na lagai thi) is baat ka inkar kya to unhon-ne kaha : main tumhen wahi hadis bayan karunga jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni. aap ke baagh ka nigraan aap ke paas umda khajoor ka aik saa laya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khajoor us ( aam ( qism ki thi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha : ye tumharey paas kahan se aain? usne kaha : main (iske) 2 saa lekar gaya aur unke iwaz maine ye aik saa khareed li, bazar mein iska narkh (rate) itna hai aur uska itna hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum par afsos ! tum ne sood ka mamla kya, jab tum ye (umda khajoor ( lena chaho to apni khajoor kisi (aur ( tijarati cheez ke iwaz farokht kar do, phir apni cheez se jo khajoor chaho , khareed lo. Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : khajoor ke iwaz khajoor , zyada laaiq hai ke sood ho, ya chandi ke iwaz chandi? ( abu-Nazara ne) kaha : main iske baad Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to unhon-ne mujhey us se mana kya aur main Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas nahi aaya. kaha : mujhey abu-Sahba ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Makka mein Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se iske barey mein sawal kya to unhon-ne bhi usey na-pasand kya tha."
4088,"Abu-Saleh se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Dinar ke badley Dinar aur dirham ke badley dirham misl-bmisl ho, jisne zyada diya ya zyada liya, us ne sood ka mamla kya. maine unse kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) to us se mukhtalif baat kehtey hain, to unhon-ne kaha : maine khud Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki aur kaha : aap ki kya raey hai, ye jo aap kehtey hain kya aap ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai ya Allah ki kitab mein paai hai? to unhon-ne kaha : na maine ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni na kitabullah mein paai, balke mujhey Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sood udhar mein hai."
4089,"Ubaidullah bin abi-Yazeed se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : mujhey Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khabar di, aap ne farmaya : (agar jinsein mukhtalif hon to ( sood udhar main hi hai."
4090,Taaus ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( mukhtalif chizon ke tabaadley mein) jo dast-badast ho usmein sood nahi hai.
4091,"Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki aur unse kaha : Sauda Sarf (naqdi ya soney chandi ke tabadley) ke hawale se aap ki apne qaul ke barey mein kya raey hai, kya aap ne ye cheez Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai ya Allah ki kitab mein paai hai? Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main unmein se koi baat nahi kehta , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tum mujh se zyada jaanney waley ho aur rahi Allah ki kitab to main (is mein) is baat ko nahi janta, albatta Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mutanabbeh raho ! sood udhaar main hi hai."
4092,"Alqama ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sood khaney aur khilaaney waley par laanat ki. kaha : maine puchha : iske likhney waley aur donon gawaahon par bhi ? unhon-ne kaha : ham sirf wo hadis bayan kartey hain jo ham ne suni hai."
4093,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sood khaney waale, khilaaney waale, likhney waley aur uske donon gawahon par laanat ki aur farmaya : (gunah mein) ye sab barabar hain."
4094,"Abdullah-bin-Numair Hamdani ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Zakariya ne Shabi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ( Shabi ne) kaha : maine unse suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, . padhi. aur Hazrat Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni donon ungliyon se apne donon kanon ki taraf ishara kya. padhi. aap farma rahe they : bila shubah halal waazeh hai aur haram waazeh hai aur un donon ke darmyan shub-haat hain logon ki badi tadaad unko nahi janti , jo shub-haat se bacha us ne apne Deen aur izzat ko bacha liya aur jo shub-haat mein pad gaya wo haram mein pad gaya, jaisey charwaha (jo ( charagaah ke ird-gird ( bakriyan ( charaata hai, qareeb hai wo us (charagaah) mein charney lagein , dekho ! har badshah ki charagaah hai. dhyan rakho ! Allah ki charagaah uski haram ki hui cheezein hain. suno! jism mein aik tukda hai, agar theek raha to Sara jism theek raha aur agar wo bigad gaya to Sara jism bigad gaya. suno! wo dil hai. (soch aur niyat se har amal ki durusti hai ya kharabi.)"
4095,Wakee aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne Zakariya se isi sanad ke sath usi ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki.
4096,is sanad se bhi uper zikr ki gaee hadis marwi hai. lekin Zakariya ki hadis un sabse zyada mukammal hai.
4097,Noman-bin-Bashir bin Sad se riwayat hai jo sahabi they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aur wo khutba sunatey they logon ko teiswin mein (eik Shahar ka naam hai Sham (Syria) mein) aur kehtey they maine suna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap farmatey they halal khula hua hai aur haram khula hua hai. phir bayan kya hadis ko isi tarah jaisey uper guzri.
4098,"Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai wo ja rahe they aik oont par jo thak gaya tha unhon-ne chaha usko aazad kar dena (yani chhod dena jangal mein) Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh se aan kar miley aur mere liye dua ki aur oont ko maara phir wo aisa chala ke wo aisa kabhi nahi chala tha (ye aap ka mojza tha). aap ne farmaya usko mere hath bech daal aik auqiya par (doosri riwayat mein panch auqiya hain aur aik auqiya zyada diya aur aik riwayat mein 2 auqiya aur aik dirham ya 2 dirham hain aur aik riwayat mein soney ka aik auqiya aur aik riwayat mein char Dinar aur Bukhari ne aik riwayat mein aath (8) so dirham aur aik riwayat mein bees Dinar aur aik riwayat mein char auqiya naql kiye hain). maine kaha nahi, phir aap ne farmaya usko mere hath bech daal. maine aik auqiya par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath bech daala aur shart ki is par sawari ki apne ghar tak. jab main apne ghar pahuncha to oont aap ke paas lekar aaya aap ne uski qeemat mere hawale ki. main lota phir aap ne mujh ko bula bheja aur farmaya kya main tujh se qeemat kam karaata tha, tera oont leney ke liye apna oont le ja aur rupya bhi tera hai."
4099,uper zikr ki gaee hadis is sanad se bhi marwi hai.
4100,"Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai maine jihad kiya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath to aap mujh se miley ( raah mein) aur meri sawari mein aik oont tha pani ka wo thak gaya tha aur bilkul chal na sakta tha. aap ne puchha terey oont ko kya hua hai? maine arz kiya wo bimar hai. ye sun kar janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) peechhey hatey aur oont ko daantaa aur uske liye dua ki phir wo hamesha sab oonton ke aagey hi chalta raha. aap ne farmaya ab tera oont kaisa hai? maine kaha achchha hai aap ki dua ki barkat se, aap ne farmaya mere hath bechtaa hai? mujhey sharm aai aur hamarey paas aur koi oont pani laney ke liye na tha aakhir maine kaha haan bechtaa hun. phir maine us oont ko aap ke hath bech daala is shart se ke main is par sawari karunga Madiney tak phir maine arz kiya : ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mein nosha hun (yani abhi mera nikah hua hai). mujhey ijazat dijiye ( logon se pahley Madina janey ki). aap ne ijazat di main logon se aagey badh kar Madina aa pahuncha wahan mere maamun miley aur oont ka haal poochha. maine sab haal bayan kiya. unhon-ne mujh ko malaamat ki (ke aik hi oont tha terey paas aur ghar waley bahut hain usko bhi tu ney bech daala aur usko ye malum na tha ke khudaawand Karim ko Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka fayda manzoor hai). Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jab maine aap se ijazat mangi to aap ne farmaya tu ney kunwari se shadi ki hai ya nikaahi se? maine kaha nikaahi se. aap ne farmaya kunwari se kyon ne ki wo tujh se khelti aur to us se kheltaa? maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! mera bap mar gaya ya Shahid ho gaya meri kai bahnein chhod kar chhoti-chhoti to mujhey bura malum hua ke main shadi karke aik aur ladki laaun unke barabar jo na unko adab sikhaaey aur na unko dabaaey. isliye maine aik nikaahi se shadi ki taake unko daabbey aur tameez sikhaaey. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina mein tashrif laey main oont subah hi ley gaya aap ne uski qeemat mujh ko di aur oont bhi pher diya."
4101,"Saalim-bin-abi-Jaad ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka (ki taraf ( se Madina aaey, to mera oont bimar ho gaya. padhi. aur unhon-ne ( unse ( mukammal qissey samet hadis bayan ki, usmein hai : phir aap ne mujh se farmaya : mujhey apna ye oont farokht kar do. maine kaha : nahi, balke wo ( waisey hi (aap hi ka hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, balke wo mujhey farokht kar do. maine kaha : nahi, aey Allah ke rasool! wo aap hi ka hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, balke usey mere hath farokht kar do. maine kaha : aik aadmi ka mere zimmey soney ka aik auqiya ( taqriban 29 giraam ( hai, iske iwaz ye aap ka hua. aap ne farmaya : maine ley liya, tum is par Madina tak pahunch jao . kaha : jab main Madina pahuncha , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : unhein aik auqiya sona aur kuchh zyada bhi do. kaha : unhon-ne mujhey aik auqiya sona diya aur aik qirat zayed diya. kaha : maine (dil mein) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye zayed Atiya mujh se kabhi alag na hoga. kaha : to wo meri thaili mein raha yahan tak ke Harra ki jang ke din ahale-Sham (Syria) ne usey (mujh se) chheen liya."
4102,"abu-Nazara ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik safar mein ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. mera oont peechhey reh gaya. padhi. aur) poori ( hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey kachokaa lagaya , phir mujh se farmaya : Allah ka naam lekar Sawar ho jao aur ye izafa bhi kiya, kaha : aap musalsal mujhey zyada ki peshkash kartey aur farmatey rahe : Allah tumhen maaf farmaey."
4103,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas aaey aur mera oont thak chuka tha to aap ne usey kachokaa lagaya , wo uchhal padaa . iske baad main uski lagaam kheenchtaa taake aap ki baat sunoon lekin main is par qaabu na pa raha tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey miley to farmaya : ye mujhey bech do. maine wo ( oont ( aapko panch auqiya ( chandi jo aik auqiya soney ke barabar thi) ke iwaz farokht kar diya. maine kaha : is shart par ke Madina tak uski peeth ( par sawari ( mere liye hogi. aap ne farmaya : Madina tak uski peeth ( par sawari ( tumhari hogi. kaha : jab main Madina pahuncha , us (oont) ko aap ke paas laya to aap ne mujhey aik auqiya ( tay shuda qeemat ka chothai hissey ( zayed diya, phir aap ne mujhey ( oont bhi) hiba (hadiya) kar diya."
4104,"abu-Mutwakkil naaji ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar kiya. padhi. mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne jangi safar kaha, padhi. aur hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye izafa kiya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jaabir ! kya tum ne poori qeemat ley li hai? maine kaha : ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qeemat bhi tumhari , oont bhi tumhara  (phir farmaya :) qeemat bhi tumhari , oont bhi tumhara."
4105,"Muaz Anbari ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Maharib se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se do auqiya aur aik ya do dirhamon mein oont khareedaa. jab aap saraar (ke maqam par) aaey to aap ne gaaey ( zabah karne) ka hukm diya, wo zabah ki gaee, logon ne usey khaya , jab aap Madina tashrif laey to aap ne mujhey hukm diya ke main masjid aaoon aur do rakatein padhun. aap ne mere liye oont ki qeemat (ke barabar soney ya chandi (ka wazan kiya aur mere liye paldaa jhukaa diya."
4106,"Khalid-bin-Haaris ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Maharib ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi qissa bayan kiya, magar unhon-ne kaha : aap ne mujh se oont qeematan khareed liya jiski unhon ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne ta'yun (nishchit) bhi ki. (is riwayat mein) unhon-ne do auqiya , aik dirham aur do dirhamon ka tazkira nahi kiya aur kaha : aap ne gaaey ka hukm diya to usey zabah kiya gaya, phir aap ne iska gosht taqseem kar diya."
4107,Ata ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : maine tumhara oont char Dinar (jo soney ke aik auqiya ke barabar hai) mein liya aur Madina tak uski peeth ( par sawari (ka haq tumhara hai.
4108,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi se baad mein adaaeygi (buzurg) ke iwaz aik nau (9) umr oont liya, aap ke paas zakat ke oont aaey to aap ne Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke wo is aadmi ko iske nau (9) umr oont ki adaaeygi kar dein. Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) lot kar aap ke paas aaey aur kaha : maine to ( aaey huey) un oonton mein saatwen saal ka bahut achchha oont hi paya hai. to aap ne farmaya : usey wahi de do, logon mein se behtreen wo hai jo ada karne mein behtreen ho."
4109,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar se riwayat hai, maine Zaid-bin-Aslam se suna, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ata-bin-Yasar ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik nau (9) umr oont baad ki adaaeygi par liya usi ki tarah. magar unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke bandon mein se behtreen wo hai jo unmein se adaaeygi mein behtreen hai."
4110,"Shoba ne hamein Salma bin kuheil se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par haq ( qarz ( tha, us ne aap ke sath sakht kalami ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ne ( usey jawab diye ka ( irada kya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ka haq ho, wo baat karta hai. aur aap ne unhein farmaya : uske liye (iske oont ka ( usi umr ka oont khareedo aur wo usey de do. unhon-ne kaha : hamein us se behtar umr ka oont hi milta hai. to aap ne farmaya : wahi khareedo aur usey de do, bila shubah tum mein se behtreen wo hai jo adaaeygi mein behtreen hai."
4111,"Ali-bin Saleh ne Salma bin kuheil se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik nai umr ka oont udhaar liya to aap ne us se behtar jawan oont diya aur farmaya : tum mein se behtreen wo hai jo adayegi mein behtreen hai."
4112,"Sufiyan ne hamein Salma bin kuheil se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi aaya, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se oont ka mutalba kar raha tha to aap ne farmaya : usey uske oont se behtar umr ka oont de do aur farmaya : tum mein se behtar wo hai jo adaaeygi mein behtar ho."
4113,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : aik ghulam aaya, us ne hijrat par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bait ki jabke aapko pata nahi chala ke wo ghulam hai. uska aaqa usey leney ke liye aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ye mujhey farokht kar do. chunanche aap ne 2 siyah ghulaamon ke iwaz usey khareed liya, phir uske baad aap kisi se bait na letey they yahan tak ke (pahley ( poochh letey : kya wo ghulam hai?"
4114,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se udhar ghalla khareeda aur aap ne usey apni zirah bataur rahan di."
4115,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne hamein Aamash se khabar di, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se ghalla khareeda aur aap ne lohey ki zirah uske haan girwi rakhi ."
4116,"abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Ibrahim Nakhai ke paas Sauda Salam mein rahan ki baat ki to unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aswad bin Yazeed ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se aainda muqarrara waqt tak adaaeygi par ghalla khareeda aur apni lohey ki zirah uske yahan girwi rakhi ."
4117,"Hafs bin Ghiyas ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Aswad ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki. padhi. aur unhon-ne lohey ki zirah ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
4118,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Amr Naqid ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Yahya ke hain, Amr ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki aur Yahya ne kaha : hamein khabar di. padhi. Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein ibne-abi najeeh se khabar di, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Kasir se, unhon-ne abu-Minhaal se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey aur wo log phalon mein aik 2 saal tak ke liye Sauda salaf kartey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo khajoor mein Sauda salaf karey to wo malum maap aur malum wazan mein malum muddat tak ke liye kare."
4119,"Abdul-Waris ne hamein ( ibne-abi najeeh ( se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin Kasir ne abu-Minhaal se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madina ( tashrif laey aur log Sauda salaf kartey they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : jo Sauda salaf karey, wo muaiyan maap aur muaiyan wazan ke baghair na kare."
4120,"Yahya-bin-Yahya, abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ismail Salim sab ne ( Sufiyan ( bin-Uena se, unhon-ne ( ibne-abi-najeeh ( se isi sanad ke sath Abdul-Waris ki hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki aur unhon-ne bhi teishuda muddat tak ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
4121,"Wakee aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi donon ne Sufiyan ( Sory ( se, unhon-ne ( ibne-abi najeeh ( se unhi ki sanad ke sath ibne-Uena ki hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki aur unhon-ne usmein muaiyan muddat tak ke alfaz ( bhi) bayan kiye."
4122,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Saeed-bin-Musaiyab hadis bayan kartey they ke Hazrat Mamar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne zakheera andozi (jama) ki wo gunahgaar hai. Saeed se kaha gaya : aap khud ( khaaney ki buniyaadi chizon ke siwa dusri cheez mein) zakheera andozi kartey hain? Saeed ne kaha : Hazrat Mamar (Raziallahu anhu) jo ye hadis bayan kartey they, wo bhi (is tarah ki) zakheera andozi (jama) kartey they."
4123,"Muhammad-bin-Ajlan ne Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Ata se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Mamar-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : gunahgaar ke siwa koi aur shakhs zakheera andozi (jama) nahi karta."
4124,"Amr-bin-Yahyaa ne Muhammad-bin-Amr se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne banu- Adi-bin-Kab ke aik fard Hazrat Mamar-bin-abi-Mamar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. aagey Yahya se Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
4125,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : qism saman ko farogh (badhotri) dene wali, (baad iske) nafe ko mitaaney wali hai."
4126,"Hazrat abu-Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : saudey mein zyada qasmein khaney se bacho kyonke wo (pahley saudey ko) farogh (badhotri) deti hai, phir ( nafe ko) mitaa deti hai."
4127,"abu-Khaisma ne hamein abu-Zubair se khabar di, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ke ghar mein ya baagh mein koi Sharik ho to usey haq nahi ke usey bechey , yahan tak ke apne Sharik ko bataaey , phir agar wo razi ho to (usey) ley-ley aur agar na-pasand karey to chhod de. (aur wo doosrey ko bech diya jaey.)"
4128,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har mushtarak (saajha) jaaidaad par, jo taqseem na hui ho Shufaa ka faisla farmaya, wo ghar ho ya baagh ho uske liye (jo iska Sharike-milkiyat hai) usey bechna jaaiz nahi yahan tak ke wo apne Sharik ko bataaey agar wo ( Sharik ( chahey to ley-ley aur agar chahey to chhod de. agar us ne (usey) farokht kar diya aur us ( Sharik ( ko itlaa na di to yahi iska zyada haqdaar hoga."
4129,"ibne-Wahab ne hamein ibne-Juraij se khabar di ke unhein abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har mushtarak (saajha) jaaidaad , zamin , ghar ya baagh mein Shufaa hai. ( kisi aik Sharik ke liye) usey farokht karna durust nahi jab tak ke wo apne Sharik ko peshkash ( na ( karey wo ( chahey to ( usey ley-ley ya chhod de. agar wo aisa na karey to uska Sharik hi iska zyada haqdaar hai jab tak ke usey bata na de."
4130,"saiyedna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi tum mein se koi apne hamsaaya (padausi) ko apni diwar mein lakdi gaadney se mana na kare.'' (kyonke ye marawwat ke khilaf hai aur apna koi nuqsan nahi balke agar hamsaaya (padausi) udhar chhat daley to us se diwar ki hifazat hai) saiyedna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they (logon se) main dekhta hun tum is hadis se dil churaatey ho, qism Allah ki ! main isko bayan karunga tum logon mein."
4131,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Yunus aur Mamar sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki."
4132,"Abbas bin Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi ne Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis kisi ne zamin ki aik baalisht ( bhi) zulm kartey huey kaat li, qiyamat ke din Allah Taala usey saat (7) zaminon se iska tauq ( bana kar) pehnaeyga."
4133,"Umar-bin Muhammad ke walid ( Muhammad-bin Zaid ( ne Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Arwa ne unke sath ghar ke kisi hissey ke barey mein jhagda kya to unhon-ne kaha : usey aur ghar ko chhod do, (jo chahey karti rahe ( maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha, aap farma rahe they : jisne haq ke baghair aik baalisht zamin bhi hasil ki, qiyamat ke din wo saat zaminon (tak) uski gardan ka tauq bana di jaeygi. (phir uski eza rasani (takleefon) se tang aa kar unhon-ne dua ki : (aey Allah ! agar ye jhooti hai to uski aankhon ko andha kar de aur uske ghar hi mein uski qabr bana de. ( Muhammad-bin Zaid ne) kaha : maine us aurat ko dekha wo andhi ho gaee thi, diwarein tatolti phirti thi aur kehti thi : mujhey Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki baddua lag gaee hai. aik martaba wo ghar mein chal rahi thi, ghar mein kuwein ke paas se guzri to usmein gir gaee aur wahi kunwan uski qabr bin gaya."
4134,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Arwa binte- ovais ne Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke khilaf dawa kya ke unhon-ne uski kuchh zamin par qabza kar liya hai aur Marwaan-bin-Hakam ke paas muqaddima lekar gaee to Hazrat Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya main is baat ke baad bhi uski zamin ke kisi hissey par qabza kar sakta hun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni? us ( Marwan ( ne kaha : aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya suna? unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jisne ( aam ya kisi ki) zamin mein se aik baalisht bhi zulm se hasil ki usey saat (7) zaminon tak ka tauq pahnaaya jaeyga to Marwan ne unse kaha : iske baad main aap se kisi shahadat ka mutalba nahi karunga . iske baad unhon ( Saeed ( ne kaha : aey Allah ! agar ye jhooti hai to uski aankhon ko andha kar de aur usey uski zamin hi mein halaak kar de. (Urwa ne) kaha : wo (is waqt tak) na miri yahan tak ke uski beenaai khatm ho gaee, phir aik martaba wo apni zamin mein chal rahi thi ke aik garhey mein ja giri aur mar gaee."
4135,"Yahya bin Zakariya-bin-abi Zayda ne hamein Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jisne zamin mein se aik baalisht bhi zulm kartey huey hasil ki qiyamat ke din usey saat zaminon se tauq pahnaaya jaeyga"
4136,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi shakhs haq ke baghair zamin ki aik baalisht (bhi) hasil nahi karta magar qiyamat ke din Allah Taala usey saat zaminon tak ka tauq pehnaeyga."
4137,"Harab bin Shaddad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se hadis bayan ki, unhein abu-Salma ne hadis bayan ki ke unke aur unki qaum ke darmyan aik zamin ke barey mein jhagda tha, wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unke samney is baat ka tazkira kya to unhon-ne kaha : abu-Salma ! zamin se kinara kash! ho jao, kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai : jisne aik baalisht barabar zamin par bhi zulm se qabza kya, usey saat (7) zaminon ka tauq pahnaaya jaeyga"
4138,"Aban ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Yahya ne hadis bayan ki ke unhein Muhammad-bin Ibrahim ne hadis bayan ki, unhein abu-Salma ne hadis bayan ki ke wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. padhi. aagey usi ki tarah bayan kya."
4139,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tumhara rastey (ki paimaaish (ke barey mein ikhtilaf ho jaey to us ( rastey ( ki chaudai saat hath rakhi jaey.
